snippet.title: Scars of Honor: Human Male character reveal in 360-degree
snippet.description:
Download the BeastBurst App 👇
🤖 Apple App Store - https://beast.ly/7fZCVjQ
🍎 Google Play Store - https://beast.ly/Nnz53Bu

👕 The Beast Burst Merch Shop - https://beast.ly/OcdIiKU

This is the official Human Male model of the upcoming MMORPG Scars of Honor. You can now fully overview the model in a 360-degree video.
Also, you can see different styles of beards and haircuts in our official Gallery: https://www.scarsofhonor.com/gallery/12

Check our website for more information about how you can Participate in the pre-alpha testing.

Don't forget to like us, share us, and hit the bell so you are always up to date with our development.
